{"tid":277583,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［無圖］唉好撚灰，旺角食麵有曱甴","createTime":"2017-06-09T17:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T07:16:07.000Z","uid":91744,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0028f58f764a9ede5547191f4049e72a5ffe8350","tid":277583,"uid":91744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母岩先去旺角食間24嘅茶記風x園<br />\n叫咗碟排骨炒麵，食咗一大半見到碟入面有隻曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當堂想嘔出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫咗個侍應過嚟問吓佢通常會點處理<br />\n點撚知佢態度好差一句閪埋嚟「茶餐廳係咁架喇唔係你想點」<br />\n哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估我第一日出街食咩，我點會唔知茶記污糟<br />\n但都唔係藉口嚟架喎，仆街你隻曱甴出現係我隻碟到仲要我食撚咗好多，真係好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾我捉到正，仲要有撚哂手手腳腳勁完整<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係想正正常常食餐飯姐唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚灰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/010331_053ebc737ca62c35fe3285d60c1c7714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F010331_053ebc737ca62c35fe3285d60c1c7714.jpg&h=e740d1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/010337_5edc7f42cf7da4a45e154288593c64f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F010337_5edc7f42cf7da4a45e154288593c64f4.jpg&h=7c1867af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97e957cb606f24f755b0ebaa760a46b3e76b9372","tid":277583,"uid":86819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"唔即刻叫食環？"},{"pid":"d9a4220696129b3f5b3d81dfb3ffce70f0e0a20c","tid":277583,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:07:58.000Z","msg":"有相就好辦事啦 報左食環未？"},{"pid":"4318675cea4b7a6104bb37e0afd30b12a40eeeff","tid":277583,"uid":863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"622414ed3ef65b47365efea772a6b943ac11b3d7","tid":277583,"uid":7824,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"Call食環啦 咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f7581d27a3370d909dd5d3e19e44cde619198a","tid":277583,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁是實茶餐廳真係咁<br />\n眼不見為乾淨，但屌你成隻曱甴屍就痴線左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都係抱住呢個心態又成日食風味園 自從有次係入面目睹隻大甲由爬黎爬去都有再食過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d635b46c7294101415ddd2b84dd10cbdb42dfd","tid":277583,"uid":91744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔即刻叫食環？</blockquote><br />\n屌打咗幾次1823冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但報咗蘋果，不過都預咗唔受理，聽朝辦公時間再打去食環再接再厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b47dcec11d8cc5572a34816db399a3272512a1","tid":277583,"uid":91744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁是實茶餐廳真係咁<br />\n眼不見為乾淨，但屌你成隻曱甴屍就痴線左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食完到而家個心勁撚唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想扣喉嘔番出嚟但嘔唔出"},{"pid":"c92fb71a3521af681416c78a0a4db5bd6975066d","tid":277583,"uid":91744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁是實茶餐廳真係咁<br />\n眼不見為乾淨，但屌你成隻曱甴屍就痴線左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都係抱住呢個心態又成日食風味園 自從有次係入面目睹隻大甲由爬黎爬去都有再食過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1e36506f01775b377280eb365a2f7e77ef75b7","tid":277583,"uid":67093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"冇左一半你仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2a95de45920141f573f1add19735d82a147bc5","tid":277583,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"好出奇呀<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/277486/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/277486/page/1</a><em></em>[/url]"},{"pid":"f3d30cdd52aa62816cb7dc04df4ef5432fe6429a","tid":277583,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/277486/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/277486/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"44cd39b6f0989ba00bebd0822fef2e8a6eb6e376","tid":277583,"uid":91744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇左一半你仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好再講落去，好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018dc376e80d85eca80ceac1b575e9808f38be3b","tid":277583,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:14:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上帝可唔可以喺香港搵到間野食乾淨嘅茶記？</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e58051ff7a1553888ad1b116c63de1797e9c687","tid":277583,"uid":91744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上帝可唔可以喺香港搵到間野食乾淨嘅茶記？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n「吓，香港啲茶廳廳不嬲係咁污糟架啦，唔係你想點呀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}